Package lt.eif.viko.amiliauskis.xslt.soap

Class TransformationServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • lt.eif.viko.amiliauskis.xslt.soap.TransformationServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransformationService
    public class TransformationServiceImpl
extends Object
implements TransformationService
    Transformation service implementation class for implementing methods from an interface class. Has six methods used for manipulating the data model - adding or removing an object from it and for returning an XML schema.
    Since:
    1.0-SNAPSHOT
    Version:
    1.0-SNAPSHOT

      • getSolarSystem

        public lt.eif.viko.amiliauskis.jaxb.model.SolarSystem getSolarSystem()
        Overridden method used for returning whole solar system XML schema for the client. Creates new JAXB and Solar system objects and uses JAXB unmarshalling tool to transform XML document to POJO. Then outputs the generated Object.
        Specified by:
        getSolarSystem in interface TransformationService
        Returns:
        solarSystem object

      • addNewInnPlanet

        public lt.eif.viko.amiliauskis.jaxb.model.SolarSystem addNewInnPlanet​(String name,
                                                                      Double mass,
                                                                      String massUnit,
                                                                      Double volume,
                                                                      Integer velocity,
                                                                      String velocityUnit,
                                                                      String type)
        Overridden method used for adding a new planet object to inner planets list. Creates a new planet object and adds values to it from the client. Then creates new SolarSystem and JAXB objects. Using JAXB unmarshalling tool transforms Solar system XML document to POJO and adds the new planet to it. After that transforms the data model back to XML and outputs it for the client.
        Specified by:
        addNewInnPlanet in interface TransformationService

        Returns:
        solarSystem object

      • deletePlanet

        public lt.eif.viko.amiliauskis.jaxb.model.SolarSystem deletePlanet​(String name)
        Overridden method used for deleting a planet specified by name. Creates new Solar system and JAXB objects and using JAXB unmarshalling tool transforms Solar system XML document to POJO. Filters out the planet which has the name attribute specified by the client and is afterwards transformed back to XML schema and returned for the client.
        Specified by:
        deletePlanet in interface TransformationService
        Parameters:
        name - string
        Returns:
        solarSystem object
